There's nothing to be done about it.

120
00:10:05.535 --> 00:10:07.295
Sir. this is
a very valuable firm.

121
00:10:07.455 --> 00:10:10.255
- Come in here.
- We've done a lot of business
with them over the years...

122
00:10:10.415 --> 00:10:12.215
